Class User

java.lang.Object
User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a user with a name, password, and budget. This class provides methods to manage user information such as updating the user's name, password, and budget, as well as methods for authenticating and displaying the user's profile.
